Description du poste
The Datalab of Saint Gobain is a team of 20 data scientists working for all the activities and businesses of the Group. The Datalab plays a crucial role in the digital transformation of the Group, and manages projects linked to Industry 4.0 (production process and supply chain optimization), and on the other hand linked to marketing and sales (algorithms for e-commerce platform and cross selling opportunities).
Within the Datalab, you will:
Collaborate with the business units to shape their needs and lead projects on various themes : production, supply chain, marketing or sales development;
